  "comment": "2inspire 200 delivers truly flexible lighting into any space, quickly and efficiently. 2inspire is a compact, silent, bright fixture in 3 sizes. These installation luminaires deliver studio-grade tuneable white light and pure theatrical quality colours. A holistically designed accessory collection easily mounts each fixture - on a wall, as a pendant, in a ceiling, or from a yoke. Innovative technology minimizes deployment costs and maximizes efficiency, making every 2inspire flexible, sustainable, and durable. This fixture features easy connection using power over ethernet.",
